description: Using NoteFolio™ Creator software, students can transfer notes between a computer and a TI-83 Plus family, TI-84 Plus family, TI-89, TI-89 Titanium, TI-92 Plus and Voyage™ 200 calulator.
summary: Using NoteFolio Creator PC software, students can transfer notes to and from their graphing calculator to Microsoft® Word® files.
author: Texas Instruments
